{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"Once upon a time,"},{"time":4000,"text":"at the age of 24,"},{"time":6000,"text":"I was a student at St. John's Medical College in Bangalore."},{"time":11000,"text":"I was a guest student during one month"},{"time":14000,"text":"of a public health course."},{"time":16000,"text":"And that changed my mindset forever."},{"time":19000,"text":"The course was good, but it was not the course content"},{"time":22000,"text":"in itself that changed the mindset."},{"time":24000,"text":"It was the brutal realization,"},{"time":26000,"text":"the first morning,"},{"time":28000,"text":"that the Indian students were better than me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"You see, I was a study nerd."},{"time":34000,"text":"I loved statistics from a young age."},{"time":36000,"text":"And I studied very much in Sweden."},{"time":38000,"text":"I used to be in the upper quarter of all courses I attended."},{"time":42000,"text":"But in St. John's, I was in the lower quarter."},{"time":46000,"text":"And the fact was that Indian students"},{"time":48000,"text":"studied harder than we did in Sweden."},{"time":51000,"text":"They read the textbook twice,"},{"time":53000,"text":"or three times or four times."},{"time":55000,"text":"In Sweden we read it once and then we went partying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58000,"text":"(Laugher)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"And that, to me,"},{"time":63000,"text":"that personal experience"},{"time":65000,"text":"was the first time in my life"},{"time":68000,"text":"that the mindset I grew up with"},{"time":70000,"text":"was changed."},{"time":73000,"text":"And I realized that perhaps"},{"time":75000,"text":"the Western world will not continue"},{"time":77000,"text":"to dominate the world forever."},{"time":80000,"text":"And I think many of you have the same sort of personal experience."},{"time":84000,"text":"It's that realization of someone you meet"},{"time":87000,"text":"that really made you change your ideas about the world."},{"time":89000,"text":"It's not the statistics, although I tried to make it funny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"And I will now,"},{"time":97000,"text":"here, onstage,"},{"time":99000,"text":"try to predict when that will happen --"},{"time":102000,"text":"that Asia will regain"},{"time":107000,"text":"its dominant position"},{"time":109000,"text":"as the leading part of the world,"},{"time":111000,"text":"as it used to be, over thousands of years."},{"time":115000,"text":"And I will do that"},{"time":117000,"text":"by trying to predict precisely"},{"time":120000,"text":"at what year"},{"time":122000,"text":"the average income per person"},{"time":124000,"text":"in India, in China, will reach that of the West."},{"time":127000,"text":"And I don't mean the whole economy,"},{"time":129000,"text":"because to grow an economy"},{"time":131000,"text":"of India to the size of U.K. --"},{"time":133000,"text":"that's a piece of cake, with one billion people."},{"time":136000,"text":"But I want to see when will the average pay, the money"},{"time":140000,"text":"for each person, per month,"},{"time":142000,"text":"in India and China,"},{"time":144000,"text":"when will that have reached that of U.K. and the United States?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"But I will start with a historical background."},{"time":151000,"text":"And you can see my map if I get it up here. You know?"},{"time":154000,"text":"I will start at 1858."},{"time":157000,"text":"1858 was a year of great technological"},{"time":161000,"text":"advancement in the West."},{"time":163000,"text":"That was the year when Queen Victoria"},{"time":166000,"text":"was able, for the first time, to communicate"},{"time":168000,"text":"with President Buchanan,"},{"time":170000,"text":"through the Transatlantic Telegraphic Cable."},{"time":173000,"text":"And they were the first to \"Twitter\" transatlantically."},{"time":176000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":177000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":181000,"text":"And I've been able, through this wonderful Google and Internet,"},{"time":184000,"text":"to find the text of the telegram"},{"time":186000,"text":"sent back from President Buchanan to Queen Victoria."},{"time":190000,"text":"And it ends like this: \"This telegraph"},{"time":193000,"text":"is a fantastic instrument to diffuse religion,"},{"time":195000,"text":"civilization, liberty and law throughout the world.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"Those are nice words. But I got sort of curious"},{"time":202000,"text":"of what he meant with liberty, and liberty for whom."},{"time":206000,"text":"And we will think about that"},{"time":208000,"text":"when we look at the wider picture of the world in 1858."},{"time":212000,"text":"Because 1858"},{"time":214000,"text":"was also watershed year"},{"time":217000,"text":"in the history of Asia."},{"time":219000,"text":"1858 was the year"},{"time":221000,"text":"when the courageous uprising"},{"time":223000,"text":"against the foreign occupation of India"},{"time":226000,"text":"was defeated by the British forces."},{"time":228000,"text":"And India was up to 89 years more of foreign domination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233000,"text":"1858 in China"},{"time":235000,"text":"was the victory in the Opium War by the British forces."},{"time":239000,"text":"And that meant that foreigners, as it said in the treaty,"},{"time":242000,"text":"were allowed to trade freely in China."},{"time":244000,"text":"It meant paying with opium for Chinese goods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"And 1858 in Japan"},{"time":250000,"text":"was the year when Japan had to sign the Harris Treaty"},{"time":253000,"text":"and accept trade on favorable condition for the U.S."},{"time":257000,"text":"And they were threatened by those black ships there,"},{"time":261000,"text":"that had been in Tokyo harbor over the last year."},{"time":263000,"text":"But, Japan, in contrast to India and China,"},{"time":267000,"text":"maintained its national sovereignty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"And let's see how much difference that can make."},{"time":273000,"text":"And I will do that by bringing these bubbles"},{"time":276000,"text":"back to a Gapminder graph here,"},{"time":278000,"text":"where you can see each bubble is a country."},{"time":281000,"text":"The size of the bubble here is the population."},{"time":284000,"text":"On this axis, as I used to have income per person in comparable dollar."},{"time":289000,"text":"And on that axis I have life expectancy, the health of people."},{"time":293000,"text":"And I also bring an innovation here."},{"time":295000,"text":"I have transformed the laser beam"},{"time":298000,"text":"into an ecological, recyclable version here, in green India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"And we will see, you know."},{"time":310000,"text":"Look here, 1858, India was here,"},{"time":313000,"text":"China was here, Japan was there,"},{"time":315000,"text":"United States and United Kingdom"},{"time":317000,"text":"was richer over there."},{"time":319000,"text":"And I will start the world like this."},{"time":322000,"text":"India was not always like this level."},{"time":324000,"text":"Actually if we go back into the historical record,"},{"time":326000,"text":"there was a time hundreds of years ago"},{"time":328000,"text":"when the income per person in India and China"},{"time":330000,"text":"was even above that of Europe."},{"time":332000,"text":"But 1850 had already been many, many years of foreign domination,"},{"time":336000,"text":"and India had been de-industrialized."},{"time":339000,"text":"And you can see that the countries who were growing"},{"time":341000,"text":"their economy was United States and United Kingdom."},{"time":343000,"text":"And they were also, by the end of the century, getting healthy,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and Japan was starting to catch up."},{"time":348000,"text":"India was trying down here."},{"time":350000,"text":"Can you see how it starts to move there?"},{"time":352000,"text":"But really, really natural sovereignty was good for Japan."},{"time":356000,"text":"And Japan is trying to move up there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358000,"text":"And it's the new century now. Health is getting better,"},{"time":360000,"text":"United Kingdom, United States."},{"time":362000,"text":"But careful now -- we are approaching the First World War."},{"time":365000,"text":"And the First World War, you know,"},{"time":367000,"text":"we'll see a lot of deaths and economical problems here."},{"time":371000,"text":"United Kingdom is going down."},{"time":373000,"text":"And now comes the Spanish flu also."},{"time":375000,"text":"And then after the First World War, they continue up."},{"time":378000,"text":"Still under foreign domination, and without sovereignty,"},{"time":381000,"text":"India and China are down in the corner."},{"time":383000,"text":"Not much has happened."},{"time":385000,"text":"They have grown their population but not much more."},{"time":387000,"text":"In the 1930's now, you can see"},{"time":389000,"text":"that Japan is going to a period of war,"},{"time":392000,"text":"with lower life expectancy."},{"time":394000,"text":"And the Second World War was really a terrible event,"},{"time":396000,"text":"also economically for Japan."},{"time":398000,"text":"But they did recover quite fast afterwards."},{"time":400000,"text":"And we are moving into the new world."},{"time":402000,"text":"In 1947 India finally"},{"time":405000,"text":"gained its independence."},{"time":407000,"text":"And they could raise the Indian flag and become a sovereign nation,"},{"time":411000,"text":"but in very big difficulties down there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":414000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"In 1949 we saw the emergence of the modern China"},{"time":421000,"text":"in a way which surprised the world."},{"time":423000,"text":"And what happened?"},{"time":425000,"text":"What happens in the after independence?"},{"time":427000,"text":"You can see that the health started to improve."},{"time":429000,"text":"Children started to go to school."},{"time":431000,"text":"Health services were provided."},{"time":433000,"text":"This is the Great Leap Forward, when China fell down."},{"time":437000,"text":"It was central planning by Mao Tse Tung."},{"time":439000,"text":"China recovered. Then they said,"},{"time":441000,"text":"\"Nevermore, stupid central planning.\""},{"time":443000,"text":"But they went up here, and India was trying to follow."},{"time":446000,"text":"And they were catching up indeed."},{"time":448000,"text":"And both countries had the better health, but still"},{"time":450000,"text":"a very low economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452000,"text":"And we came to 1978, and Mao Tse Tung died,"},{"time":455000,"text":"and a new guy turned up from the left."},{"time":458000,"text":"And it was Deng Xiaoping coming out here."},{"time":461000,"text":"And he said, \"Doesn't matter"},{"time":463000,"text":"if a cat is white or black,"},{"time":465000,"text":"as long as it catches mice.\""},{"time":467000,"text":"Because catching mice"},{"time":469000,"text":"is what the two cats wanted to do."},{"time":472000,"text":"And you can see the two cats being here,"},{"time":475000,"text":"China and India, wanting to catch the mices over there, you know."},{"time":478000,"text":"And they decided to go not only for health and education,"},{"time":481000,"text":"but also starting to grow their economy."},{"time":483000,"text":"And the market reformer was successful there."},{"time":485000,"text":"In '92 India follows with a market reform."},{"time":488000,"text":"And they go quite closely together,"},{"time":490000,"text":"and you can see that the similarity with India and China,"},{"time":492000,"text":"in many ways, are greater than the differences with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"And here they march on. And will they catch up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":497000,"text":"This is the big question today."},{"time":499000,"text":"There they are today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"Now what does it mean that the --"},{"time":503000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":506000,"text":"the averages there -- this is the average of China."},{"time":509000,"text":"If I would split China, look here,"},{"time":511000,"text":"Shanghai has already catched up."},{"time":514000,"text":"Shanghai is already there."},{"time":516000,"text":"And it's healthier than the United States."},{"time":520000,"text":"But on the other hand, Guizhou, one of the poorest"},{"time":523000,"text":"inland provinces of China, is there."},{"time":526000,"text":"And if I split Guizhou into urban and rural,"},{"time":530000,"text":"the rural part of Guizhou goes down there."},{"time":533000,"text":"You see this enormous inequity in China,"},{"time":536000,"text":"in the midst of fast economic growth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538000,"text":"And if I would also look at India,"},{"time":540000,"text":"you have another type of inequity, actually, in India."},{"time":543000,"text":"The geographical, macro-geographical difference is not so big."},{"time":548000,"text":"Uttar Pradesh, the biggest of the states here,"},{"time":550000,"text":"is poorer and has a lower health than the rest of India."},{"time":553000,"text":"Kerala is flying on top there,"},{"time":556000,"text":"matching United States in health,"},{"time":558000,"text":"but not in economy."},{"time":560000,"text":"And here, Maharashtra, with Mumbai,"},{"time":562000,"text":"is forging forward."},{"time":564000,"text":"Now in India, the big inequities are within the state,"},{"time":567000,"text":"rather than between the states."},{"time":569000,"text":"And that is not a bad thing, in itself."},{"time":572000,"text":"If you have a lot inequity, macro-geographical inequities"},{"time":576000,"text":"can be more difficult in the long term to deal with,"},{"time":579000,"text":"than if it is in the same area where you have a growth center"},{"time":582000,"text":"relatively close to where poor people are living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585000,"text":"No, there is one more inequity. Look there, United States."},{"time":588000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":589000,"text":"Oh, they broke my frame."},{"time":591000,"text":"Washington, D.C. went out here."},{"time":594000,"text":"My friends at Gapminder wanted me to show this"},{"time":597000,"text":"because there is a new leader in Washington"},{"time":599000,"text":"who is really concerned about the health system."},{"time":601000,"text":"And I can understand him, because Washington, D.C."},{"time":604000,"text":"is so rich over there"},{"time":607000,"text":"but they are not as healthy as Kerala."},{"time":609000,"text":"It's quite interesting, isn't it?"},{"time":611000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":616000,"text":"I can see a business opportunity for Kerala,"},{"time":619000,"text":"helping fix the health system in the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":623000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"Now here we have the whole world. You have the legend down there."},{"time":628000,"text":"And when you see the two giant cats here, pushing forward,"},{"time":632000,"text":"you see that in between them"},{"time":634000,"text":"and ahead of them,"},{"time":636000,"text":"is the whole emerging economies of the world,"},{"time":638000,"text":"which Thomas Friedman so correctly called the \"flat world.\""},{"time":642000,"text":"You can see that in health and education,"},{"time":644000,"text":"a large part of the world population is putting forward,"},{"time":647000,"text":"but in Africa, and other parts,"},{"time":649000,"text":"as in rural Guizhou in China,"},{"time":651000,"text":"there is still people with low health and very low economy."},{"time":654000,"text":"We have an enormous disparity in the world."},{"time":656000,"text":"But most of the world in the middle are pushing forwards very fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661000,"text":"Now, back to my projections."},{"time":663000,"text":"When will it catch up? I have to go back to very conventional graph."},{"time":668000,"text":"I will show income per person on this axis instead,"},{"time":671000,"text":"poor down here, rich up there."},{"time":673000,"text":"And then time here, from 1858"},{"time":675000,"text":"I start the world."},{"time":677000,"text":"And we shall see what will happen with these countries."},{"time":680000,"text":"You see, China under foreign domination"},{"time":683000,"text":"actually lowered their income and came down to the Indian level here."},{"time":686000,"text":"Whereas U.K. and United States is getting richer and richer."},{"time":690000,"text":"And after Second World War, United States is richer than U.K."},{"time":693000,"text":"But independence is coming here."},{"time":695000,"text":"Growth is starting, economic reform."},{"time":697000,"text":"Growth is faster, and with projection from IMF"},{"time":700000,"text":"you can see where you expect them to be in 2014."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704000,"text":"Now, the question is, \"When will the catch up take place?\""},{"time":709000,"text":"Look at, look at the United States."},{"time":711000,"text":"Can you see the bubble?"},{"time":713000,"text":"The bubbles, not my bubbles,"},{"time":715000,"text":"but the financial bubbles."},{"time":717000,"text":"That's the dot com bubble. This is the Lehman Brothers doorstep there."},{"time":722000,"text":"You see it came down there."},{"time":724000,"text":"And it seems this is another rock coming down there, you know."},{"time":729000,"text":"So they doesn't seem to go this way, these countries."},{"time":732000,"text":"They seem to go in a more humble growth way, you know."},{"time":735000,"text":"And people interested in growth"},{"time":737000,"text":"are turning their eyes towards Asia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"I can compare to Japan. This is Japan coming up."},{"time":743000,"text":"You see, Japan did it like that."},{"time":745000,"text":"We add Japan to it."},{"time":747000,"text":"And there is no doubt that fast catch up"},{"time":750000,"text":"can take place."},{"time":752000,"text":"Can you see here what Japan did?"},{"time":754000,"text":"Japan did it like this, until full catch up,"},{"time":756000,"text":"and then they follow with the other high-income economies."},{"time":760000,"text":"But the real projections for those ones,"},{"time":763000,"text":"I would like to give it like this."},{"time":768000,"text":"Can be worse, can be better."},{"time":770000,"text":"It's always difficult to predict, especially about the future."},{"time":774000,"text":"Now, a historian tells me it's even more difficult to predict about the past."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":779000,"text":"I think I'm in a difficult position here."},{"time":782000,"text":"Inequalities in China and India"},{"time":784000,"text":"I consider really the big obstacle"},{"time":788000,"text":"because to bring the entire population into growth and prosperity"},{"time":792000,"text":"is what will create a domestic market,"},{"time":794000,"text":"what will avoid social instability,"},{"time":797000,"text":"and which will make use of the entire capacity"},{"time":800000,"text":"of the population."},{"time":802000,"text":"So, social investments in health, education and infrastructure,"},{"time":806000,"text":"and electricity is really what is needed in India and China."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"You know the climate. We have great international experts"},{"time":815000,"text":"within India telling us that the climate is changing,"},{"time":818000,"text":"and actions has to be taken,"},{"time":820000,"text":"otherwise China and India would be the countries"},{"time":823000,"text":"most to suffer from climate change."},{"time":825000,"text":"And I consider India and China the best partners in the world"},{"time":828000,"text":"in a good global climate policy."},{"time":831000,"text":"But they ain't going to pay"},{"time":833000,"text":"for what others, who have more money,"},{"time":835000,"text":"have largely created, and I can agree on that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838000,"text":"But what I'm really worried about is war."},{"time":841000,"text":"Will the former rich countries really accept"},{"time":843000,"text":"a completely changed world economy,"},{"time":846000,"text":"and a shift of power away from where it has been"},{"time":849000,"text":"the last 50 to 100 to 150 years,"},{"time":851000,"text":"back to Asia?"},{"time":853000,"text":"And will Asia be able to handle that"},{"time":855000,"text":"new position of being in charge"},{"time":857000,"text":"of being the most mighty, and the governors of the world?"},{"time":860000,"text":"So, always avoid war,"},{"time":862000,"text":"because that always pushes human beings backward."},{"time":865000,"text":"Now if these inequalities, climate and war can be avoided,"},{"time":869000,"text":"get ready for a world in equity,"},{"time":872000,"text":"because this is what seems to be happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":875000,"text":"And that vision that I got as a young student,"},{"time":877000,"text":"1972, that Indians can be much better than Swedes,"},{"time":883000,"text":"is just about to happen."},{"time":885000,"text":"And it will happen precisely"},{"time":888000,"text":"the year 2048"},{"time":892000,"text":"in the later part of the summer, in July,"},{"time":895000,"text":"more precisely, the 27th of July."},{"time":898000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":906000,"text":"The 27th of July, 2048"},{"time":910000,"text":"is my 100th birthday."},{"time":912000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":914000,"text":"And I expect to speak"},{"time":916000,"text":"in the first session of the 39th TED India."},{"time":920000,"text":"Get your bookings in time. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":923000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}